org.spongepowered.api.item.inventory.entity

Interface UserInventory<T extends User>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CarriedInventory<T>, Inventory, Iterable<Inventory>, Nameable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    PlayerInventory

    public interface UserInventory<T extends User>
extends CarriedInventory<T>
    Represents the inventory of a User. It consists of a MainPlayerInventory (containing the main GridInventory and the Hotbar) and an EquipmentInventory
